<p class="has-medium-font-size"><strong>Technology</strong></p>
<p>We Dwell Below roughly has four parts involved: 1) Chewing Device, 2) Multiuser (networking) system in Unity, 3) Costumes, 4) Story.</p>
<div class="wp-block-image">
<figure class="aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" width="1024" height="713" src="/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/system-1024x713.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-2767" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/system-1024x713.jpg 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/2019/02/system-300x209.jpg 300w, /wp-content/uploads/2019/02/system-768x535.jpg 768w, /wp-content/uploads/2019/02/system-400x279.jpg 400w, /wp-content/uploads/2019/02/system-210x146.jpg 210w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>
</div>
<p class="has-medium-font-size"><strong>Chewing Device</strong></p>
<p>For this project, I need to redesign the one used with Google Cardboard + web browser completely, for it to work with HTC Vive + Unity3D. I laser-cut the base and used leather for strong strap in the end. Circular pressure sensor (FSR) for the input.</p>
