<p>In 2018, we brought the project back to England again, this time<a rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" a two day installation in The Great North Museum: Hancock in Newcastle (opens in a new tab)" href="https://www.andfestival.org.uk/blog/we-dwell-below-documentation/" target="_blank"> a two day installation in The Great North Museum: Hancock in Newcastle</a>. The participants are mostly kids this time! :D</p>
